sx.blah.discord.api.events

Interface IListener<T extends Event>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The event type to handle.
    Functional Interface:
    This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.

    @FunctionalInterface
public interface IListener<T extends Event>
    Used to represent a class that handles only one event. WARNING: Due to an issue in TypeTools, using this class through a lambda expression *may* slow your bot down.
